  "page": "Captain-general",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Captain-general</b> is the highest rank in the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_incumbents\">Known incumbents</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Captain-general&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known incumbents\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Aegor_Rivers\" title=\"Aegor Rivers\">Aegor \"Bittersteel\" Rivers</a>, founder of the Golden Company. One of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Bastards\" title=\"Great Bastards\">Great Bastards</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_IV_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon IV Targaryen\">King Aegon the Unworthy</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Blackfyre_(cousin_of_Maelys_I)\" title=\"Daemon Blackfyre (cousin of Maelys I)\">Daemon Blackfyre</a>, collateral descendant of Bittersteel through his namesake <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon I Blackfyre</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maelys_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Maelys I Blackfyre\">Maelys \"the Monstrous\" Blackfyre</a>, Daemon's cousin and successor. One of the <a href=\"/index.php/Band_of_Nine\" title=\"Band of Nine\">Ninepenny Kings</a> who attempted to <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Ninepenny_Kings\" title=\"War of the Ninepenny Kings\">conquer</a> the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a>.</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Toyne\" title=\"Myles Toyne\">Myles \"Blackheart\" Toyne</a>, an exiled knight of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Toyne\" title=\"House Toyne\">House Toyne</a> with an erroneous cruel reputation.</li>\n<li>Ser \"Homeless\" <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a>, Toyne's successor. Served as <a href=\"/index.php/Paymaster\" title=\"Paymaster\">paymaster</a> before he was made captain-general after the death of Blackheart.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Captain-general&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, The Lost Lord.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404062719\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 124/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 447/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 529/5000000 bytes\n-->\